query.esql:
FROM {{indexPattern}}
| WHERE k8s.pod.name IS NOT NULL AND k8s.pod.phase IS NOT NULL AND k8s.namespace.name IS NOT NULL
| STATS 
    last_seen_ts = MAX(@timestamp),
    latest_phase = MAX(k8s.pod.phase) BY k8s.pod.name, k8s.namespace.name, k8s.node.name
| WHERE latest_phase == 2
| EVAL phase_name = CASE(
    latest_phase == 1, "pending",
    latest_phase == 2, "running",
    latest_phase == 3, "succeeded",
    latest_phase == 4, "failed",
    "unknown"
  ), last_seen = DATE_DIFF("seconds", last_seen_ts, NOW())
| EVAL Pod=k8s.pod.name, Namespace=k8s.namespace.name, Phase=phase_name, last_seen_ts, Node=k8s.node.name
| KEEP Pod, Namespace, Node,Phase, last_seen, last_seen_ts
| SORT last_seen ASC

config.title: Last Seen Running Pods by Node

query.esql:
FROM {{indexPattern}}
| WHERE k8s.pod.name IS NOT NULL AND k8s.node.name IS NOT NULL AND k8s.pod.phase == 2
| STATS 
    last_seen_ts = MAX(@timestamp),
    podCount = COUNT_DISTINCT(k8s.pod.name) BY Node=k8s.node.name    
| EVAL last_update = DATE_DIFF("seconds", last_seen_ts, NOW())
| KEEP Node, podCount,last_update
| SORT podCount DESC
